node.text: ⚠️AMAZING KITTEN RESCUE!⚠️ During our recent trip to Greece, my friends @everchanginghorizon and @jess.wandering rescued the cutest little kitten that was abandoned on a cliffside and I was honored to be able to help too after getting introduced to @zawf.zante.gr an incredible animal rescue charity that desperately needed more funding to help save more animals! I donated 1,000 euros to them on the spot, but we have also created a @karmagawa fundraiser with the goal of raising $25,000 to get them a full on shelter and veterinarian on their staff because there are SO many more animals in Zakynthos that need URGENT help so please donate what you can, share this video with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see and share this too and let’s all work together to raise the $25k ZAWF needs to help more animals in need! Sadly, this little kitten didn’t make it and that’s why we MUST get these poor animals more help faster in the future…see my stories for the link to the @karmagawa Facebook fundraiser and ALL donations great and small are most appreciated! #helpanimals #savethekitties #zakynthos #animalrescue

node.text: ⚠️SHARE TO HELP SAVE OUR PLANET BEFORE IT’S TOO LATE⚠️Repost from @karmagawa We humans are destroying our environment and wildlife in so many different ways as this sad but accurate cartoon replaces the roles of humans and animals in today’s society to show us all a different perspective and if there’s any hope of saving our planet and too many endangered species before it’s too late, then we MUST confront these issues RIGHT NOW and that starts with education and spreading awareness to everyone! So, watch this video a few times as it covers many of the methods in which we’re destroying the only planet we all have and really think about its message because it’s 100% true and sadly it’s future generations of humans and animals that will suffer the greatest consequences of our irresponsible behavior, especially if we do nothing and allow all of this destruction to continue. We MUST work together and fight for our planet and our wildlife so please share this video with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers in the comments who need to see it and share it with their followers too — it’s not too late for us to change our ways, all our wildlife and our planet deserves it! Great video by Steve Cutts and music by Kina #saveourplanet #climatechange #globalwarming #endanimalcruelty #karmagawa

node.text: Repost from @karmagawa Here’s why we are SO proud for Karmagawa to support animal rescue centers like @animalaid_india all over the world as they help so many animals in need! Please share this video with your followers and tag people, influencers and celebrities who need to see it as four small puppies came close to losing their lives in a horrendous accident when they stumbled into spilled tar in a garbage pile, but thanks to the hard work of some kind-hearted individuals these puppies were saved! When the first one wandered in and got stuck in the tar, she must have cried so much that the others came to see what was the matter, and they too got glued down by the awful tar. We knew they had a mother, but we couldn't find her until the day after their rescue and the hours-long process of removing the tar with oil and dish soap. These poor puppies were dazed with confusion, pain, fear and frustration, and two were so completely covered that all they could move was their eyes. But by the time Mommy arrived, they were freed from the poisonous grip of the tar and ready for the comfort of her love! We ALL must do what we can to help animals whenever possible…share this story with your followers and let’s inspire everyone to make this a better planet for humans and animals alike! #helpanimals #kindnessmatters #karmagawa

node.title: Saving Puppies From A Tragic Accident

President Ashraf Ghani fled the country as the Taliban took over the presidential palace and the government collapsed and now gunfire and fear has now gripped the city, with tens of thousands of people trying to escape and witnesses say at least 5 people have died so far following desperate scenes at Kabul airport. With all scheduled flights now suspended, many foreigners and Afghans are now stranded as the militants' return to rule brings an end to almost 20 years of a US-led coalition's presence in the country. Please join us in praying for all the people and families now stuck in Afghanistan and share this post with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see and share this too as we must make EVERYONE aware of what’s happening here to get them help RIGHT NOW! node.text: It’s actually pretty sad the kind of narrow-minded messages I’m getting after our recent international @karmagawa fundraisers for hard-hit countries like Greece, Turkey, Algeria and now Haiti as too many people mistakenly believe we should donate ONLY to issues affecting the United States. We already have several US charity projects along with new upcoming projects in New York, Connecticut, Florida, California, Colorado and Texas to name a few, but we also recognize that we’re ALL ON THE SAME PLANET TOGETHER and the devastating wildfires in Europe and now the earthquake in Haiti requires us to spread awareness and raise as much funds as possible to help them in their time of need. We REALLY must leave narrow-mindedness behind and unite as one people to make this a planet we can ALL be proud of! #weareone #dontbenarrowminded #cmonpeople #karmagawa #letsunite

node.text: ⚠️SAD NEWS, PLEASE SHARE AND LET’S HELP THOSE IN NEED RIGHT NOW!⚠️ I am SO proud of the @karmagawa and @savethereef communities for now raising $60,000+ in less than a week to help the hard hit communities of Greece and Turkey and I have 2 announcements to help even more, 1.) we’re adding Algeria to the list of countries to donate to after 65 people there were just killed by wildfires and 2.) we at @karmagawa will be matching the $60,000+ already raised dollar-for-dollar thanks to my recent trading profits and 100% of the profits from our charity apparel designed by my Karmagawa co-founder @badboi so that we’ll be donating at least $120,000+ to help as there are sadly hundreds of wildfires burning in these countries right now! Our fundraiser is ongoing so please keep donating and sharing posts about this crisis to help spread awareness as these countries need all the help they can get right now since tens of thousands of people have already lost everything, dozens have died along with countless animals, there are now mass evacuations and entire communities have burned to the ground so we are raising funds to help those affected with food, water, shelter and medical treatment in their time of need...we appreciate ALL donations great and small and even if you can't donate, please share this fundraiser as every last share also helps! #givingback #helpthoseinneed #helpgreece #helpturkey #helpalgeria #wildfire

node.text: ⚠️SAD NEWS, PLEASE SHARE AND LET’S SAVE OUR PLANET BEFORE IT’S TOO LATE!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa Wildfires have erupted around the world; the most devastating the past few days in Turkey, but also Italy, USA, Spain, Russia, France, Cyprus, Finland, Lebanon, Canada & Greece have also had terrible fires! There has also been severe flooding in Germany, China, Italy, Belgium & Netherlands and now hail bigger than tennis balls has rained down in northern Italy…and it’s even snowed in Brazil! The second largest river in South America, Paraná River, is currently suffering from a severe drought, and we’ve seen tornadoes in the Czech Republic. The death toll from all these events is rising fast and more and more people are being evacuated and displaced from their homes as sadly these are all consequences of the irresponsible way we treat our one and only planet…WE MUST CHANGE OUR WAYS BEFORE IT’S TOO LATE! Please share this post with your followers, use your social media platform to spread awareness about this, tag your friends, celebrities, influencers, help us get the word out RIGHT NOW! PS we’ve had countless messages from our wonderful Turkish followers asking to share this and to all of them, our thoughts and prayers are with you, your families and your friends and we’re going to do everything possible to get the word out and get you more international aid! Thx @earthfocus #helpturkey #prayforturkey #helptheplanet #savetheplanet #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️SAD BREAKING NEWS, PLEASE SHARE AND JOIN US IN PRAYING FOR TURKEY!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa Nearly 60 raging wildfires have broken out in Southern Turkey as temperatures have soared and strong winds stoked the flames the past 2 days, killing at least 4 people along with 1,000+ farm animals and sending 60 more people to the hospital as their homes burned down. So far 18 villages have been evacuated and 35 aircrafts, 457 vehicles, and 4,000 personnel have been involved in the firefighting efforts, as separate wildfires raged in the provinces of Osmaniye, Kayseri, Kocaeli, Adana, Mersin and Kutahya. Turkey has battled a series of disasters caused by extreme weather conditions this summer, including flash floods last week that killed 6 people in the Black Sea region so please join us in praying for all the people and animals in these hard hit communities along with the brave firefighters and share this with your followers and tag people, celebrities and influencers who need to see and share this too as we need as many prayers as possible right now! #prayforturkey #wildfire #wildfires #staysafeeveryone #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️PLEASE SHARE WITH YOUR FOLLOWERS TO STOP THIS, ANIMALS DESERVE FAR BETTER!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa At an equestrian center in Murcia, Spain, summer classes are being offered to children with various craft activities, one of which is painting a horse. THIS IS WRONG ON SO MANY LEVELS — horses are NOT objects to be used by humans and animals should NOT be used for entertainment! WE MUST STOP forcing innocent animals to be treated like this and instead learn to respect these beautiful creatures much more! On top of that, we must teach our children that animals deserve our love, compassion and respect, not that they can be used as objects to be painted on. Please use your social media platform for good and share this sad video with your followers and tag people, celebrities, influencers news media who need to see and share this too as we must make EVERYONE aware that no animal deserves to be treated like this and our children must be taught better values in life! #stopanimalcruelty #endanimalcruelty #animalsdeservebetter #horsesarelife #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️URGENT ISSUE, PLEASE SHARE AND DONATE TO OUR NEW FUNDRAISER TO HELP RESCUE MORE ANIMALS! ⚠️Repost from @karmagawa and dog rescuer @ms.mojorising_ who says: I’m posting this again because it’s too severe of an issue not to. Not only is it a severe issue in El Paso….but it has become the norm. This heartbreaking scene is what happens day in and day out here. All those dogs y’all see me move out of state is for this exact reason, because heartless people don’t think or care. They didn’t measure the responsibility that being a pet owner requires and instead of taking responsibility/reaching out for help from a rescue they opt to dump their poor dog. I am disgusted, I am furious, and I am heartbroken. El Paso needs to DO BETTER! The person recording this video is a fellow dog rescuer and after recording she called El Paso Sheriffs Department, was given a case number, and secured the husky. The last time I was updated, the husky is safe at the sheriff’s department and will be taken in by Huckleberry Hound Dog Rescue of El Paso. TOO MANY DOGS ARE NOT AS LUCKY TO BE RESCUED SO WE MUST WORK TOGETHER TO TREAT ANIMALS BETTER! Please donate to our new Karmagawa fundraiser linked on this post to help Esmerelda and other incredible rescuers save more animals in need and whether you do or don’t donate you can also help by sharing this post with your followers and tagging people, celebrities and influencers who need to see and share it too as we must all use our social media platforms to remind everyone to take better care of their pets, do NOT just leave them on the side of the road like this…THIS IS VERY CRUEL! #savethedogs #stopanimalcruelty #endanimalcruelty #petsarefamily #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️TWO NEW KARMAGAWA SCHOOL ALERTS!⚠️ I’m SO excited to announce that 2 more @karmagawa schools will be opening next week in Bali and they will be our 87th and 88th schools/libraries built! Sadly, our pace of new projects has slowed down a bit lately as there’s been a lockdown in Bali which has pushed back construction/openings, but with the lockdown officially over on July 25th so. these 2 new schools will finally have their grand openings! Here’s a sneak peak at both kindergartens and notice how each new school comes with an incredible mural designed to raise awareness for the children to learn about environmental destruction at an early age…it truly is our youth who must be educated about these important issues like @savethereef as they’ll sadly be the ones facing the greatest consequences in the coming years. Swipe through these photos and see we’ve also converted some of our most recent $200,000 donation to @balichildrensproject to help feed 250 families in need and my @karmagawa co-founder @badboi and I can’t encourage everyone enough to go to the @balichildrensproject website and donate what you can too as Bali has been hit extremely hard lately and there are SO MANY families that need help right now so all donations, great and small, are most appreciated. Stay tuned for more details about these new schools next week and I hope you have a great/safe weekend! #newschool #givingback #charity #karmagawa

node.text: ⚠️SAD BREAKING NEWS: PLEASE JOIN US IN PRAYING FOR EVERYONE IN THESE HARD HIT AREAS!⚠️ Repost from @karmagawa We need as many prayers as possible right now because in the last few days, over 200 people have died due to severe flash flooding in Germany, Belgium, Austria, Switzerland, Luxembourg and parts of the Netherlands with hundreds more missing and nearly 1,000 injured as Europe is suffering the worst flooding devastation in several decades. And now today, at least 12 people have died in the city of Zhengzhou, China due to record-breaking rainfall and catastrophic flooding, and more than 100,000 people have been forced to flee to seek safety. Many factors contribute to flooding, but a warming atmosphere caused by climate change makes extreme rainfall more likely so we MUST TREAT OUR PLANET BETTER BEFORE IT’S TOO LATE! Please share this post with your followers and tag people who need to see it as heavy rain is forecast to continue and we must use our social media platforms to thank all the rescue workers of their brave efforts, to pray for more survivors and make sure everyone takes the proper precautions to stay safe! #flashflood #flooding #climatechange #prayforbelgium #prayforgermany #prayforchina #karmagawa

node.text: Happy birthday to my mom today as she is literally the best mom I, or anyone else, could ever ask for! Everything I am and everything I achieve in life is due to her incredible love, dedication, sacrifice and her heartfelt guidance over the years, not to mention the self-confidence she’s helped instill in me. Because she taught me to always believe in myself and that I could achieve anything I wanted in life (as long as I dreamt big and worked my butt off every day) and her nonstop caring for me is something I’m truly grateful for. To those who say I just got lucky in the stock market, I say the harder I’ve worked the luckier I’ve gotten over the years, just like my now 20+ millionaire students too! But I definitely owe my crazy work ethic to my mom, so I guess they’re not wrong that I am very lucky in life — they just don’t realize my luck all comes down to having such an incredible mom and dad behind me all these years…and in the future as we’re a family business too! And I love how many of my students and friends know my mom too so I’d appreciate everyone wishing her a happy birthday in the comments here so she can see just how many people we’re able to reach through my stock market lessons and now with the amazing @karmagawa and @savethereef communities too! #happybirthday #bestmomever #ilovemymom #mommasboy
